snippet.textDisplay:
I've been asking for purple since Alien and here it is! Reaction until opening: YAAAAAAASS!! (Also, that crown mirror is epic!).

Then I saw it: such pretty shades..but. I'm so sad there aren't any purple shades in the colour of the gorgeous packaging (the velvet and the paper)- the royal purple- and a shimmer in that tone, maybe a tad lighter or darker? I'm definitely missing some iconic purple shades.

However the swatches had me drooling (blood queen, and the last two swatches are my favourite), so I might splurge after all. All these palettes on the market are 13 in a dozen and only Jeffree comes with interesting stuff that's also not specifically "on trend", but just gorgeous!
